SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS from_company, MIN(lt.link) AS movie_link_type, MIN(t.title) AS non_polish_sequel_movie
FROM company_name AS cn,
 company_type AS ct,
 keyword AS k,
 link_type AS lt,
 movie_companies AS mc,
 movie_keyword AS mk,
 movie_link AS ml,
 title AS t
WHERE lt.id = ml.link_type_id
 AND ml.movie_id = t.id
 AND t.id = mk.movie_id
 AND mk.keyword_id = k.id

AND cn.country_code != '[gb]'
AND (cn.name LIKE '%CBS%' OR cn.name LIKE '%Broadcasting%')
AND ct.kind = 'distributors'
AND k.keyword = 'murder'
AND lt.link LIKE '%featured%'
AND mc.note IS NULL
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1961 AND 2006;
